# Publish exclusions

When publishing or packaging this site for server upload, **do not include**:

| Folder | Reason |
|---|---|
| `node_modules` | npm build tooling; no page references |
| `build` | AdminLTE grunt/less sources only |
| `HomeCss` | unused; no page references |
| `new_assets` (top-level) | duplicate of `user/new_assets` |
| `App_Data` | VS PublishProfiles only |
| `.git`, `.vs`, `obj` | IDE / VCS noise |

Prefer running `publish.ps1` from the repo root — it strips these after precompile.

**Keep** runtime folders: `bower_components`, `dist`, `plugins`, `sarah`, `web-assets`, `site`, `admin`, `user`, `Franchisee`, `Bin`, `assets`, `css`, `js`, `img`, `MyJs`, `content`, `Operatorimage`, `Webservices`, `App_Code`.
